<plot>To some they are a lost generation -- The Way Forward documents the lives of three teenage girls growing up in post-apartheid South Africa. To succeed in the face of significant obstacles, each must reconcile her dreams for the future with her current circumstances. In the end, only one fully achieves her goals.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?600118</url></doc>
